    <item>
      <title>尽管选举临近，俄罗斯通胀率有所上升，但短期内难以缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/russian-inflation-to-offer-little-relief-before-election-despite-rate-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使政策制定者为了控制物价增长而将借贷成本提高了一倍多，俄罗斯的通货膨胀也不太可能让官员们在总统选举前得到喘息的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/russian-inflation-to-offer-little-relief-before-election-despite-rate-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 07:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>打击胡塞武装增加中东风险，油价突破 80 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其盟国对也门胡塞叛乱分子发动空袭，以报复红海船只遭受袭击，这些袭击危及了通过重要水道的燃料和货物流动，油价大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 23:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在 X 帐户被黑客入侵之前，SEC 的网络记录令人担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/sec-had-a-fraught-cyber-record-long-before-x-account-was-hacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，美国证券交易委员会 X 账户遭到黑客攻击，揭示了一个令人不安的事实：华尔街首席监管机构的网络安全措施一再被发现缺乏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/sec-had-a-fraught-cyber-record-long-before-x-account-was-hacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 19:25:53 GMT</pubDate>
